  <brief_title>Efficacy of a Behavioral Based Education Intervention to Decrease Medication History Errors Among Professional Nurses.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy of a Behavioral Based Education Intervention to Decrease Medication History Errors Among Professional Nurses.</official_title>
